metadata.name: The Sushi Master
metadata.description:
They say "the journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step". This sushi chef has been in the industry for over 15 years, working his way up before opening his own restaurant. 

First Step is a collection of post-processed photographs by bullishNFT.   There will be a maximum of 100 1/1 images in this collection. 

No utility and no roadmap.
